// ---------------------------------------------------------------
// Personality beat — a short trait phrase. Callable on its own or
// folded into a quote.
// ---------------------------------------------------------------
Table: Personality
quick to laugh and quicker to haggle
suspicious of strangers but fair once trust is earned
endlessly chatty about the weather and the roads
gruff, efficient, and impatient with browsers
warm and grandmotherly, always offering tea
sharp-eyed for a thief and proud of it
distracted, often mid-thought about something else entirely
unfailingly polite in a way that feels rehearsed
boastful about the quality of the stock
nervous, glancing often toward the back room
dry-humoured and slow to smile
generous with advice, stingy with discounts
